# Resolved stdlib snapshot — materialised by `cyrius deps` from the
# version-pinned toolchain (cyrius.cyml [package].cyrius). Never committed:
# a vendored copy goes stale vs the pinned compiler's own stdlib (the
# "cwd ./lib/ shadows version-pinned …" build note). CI runs `cyrius deps`.
